# Individual Report Structure

## 1. Introduction

Introduce the Cyber Shield project, the cyber-safety topic and your role in the group.

## 2. Project Planning and Teamwork

Explain how the group organised meetings, tasks and communication.

## 3. Personal Contribution

Explain your individual work such as coding, testing, design or documentation.

## 4. Prototype Development

Explain how the prototype improved from Version 1 to Version 2.

## 5. Communication and Collaboration Reflection

Reflect on teamwork, communication and problem solving.

## 6. Professional Development

Explain what skills and knowledge you developed during the project.

## 7. AI Use Statement

Explain how AI tools were used during development.

## 8. Appendices

Include supporting evidence such as screenshots, meeting minutes and testing results.
